Question: Explain to a younger friend how to apply for a college.
Answer:
First, you should have a list of places you want to go. The process for applying is relatively typical. You will go to the website where they will usually ask for you to fill out qn application online. There is your basic information. But you will need your parents because you will be asked about family income. There is usually an essay or two. Be creative and be honest. The essays are where colleges look for people to stand out. You will need information from high school. You cwn get the school to send transcripts out for you. 